summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to and amending Plat 45W, Page 118 of the Official Zoning Map of the City of Seattle, Ordinance 86300, to rezone certain property in Block 8, Jackson St. Addition to the City of Seattle from Duplex Residence High Density (RD 5000) Zone to Community Business (BC) Zone (Petition of Noble A. and O.E. Welch, C.F. 289162).
